34
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,160
Let's have dinner tomorrow evening.

35
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,640
Dinner?

36
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,640
I know a great restaurant.

37
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,280
My treat.

38
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,040
Let me pay, Mr. Xu.

39
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,520
You helped to look for my parents.

40
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,560
You're welcome.

41
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:02,680
Tomorrow is my birthday.

42
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:03,800
It is?

43
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:05,680
Go.

44
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:06,520
OK.

45
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,720
I haven't had this much fun
for a long time!

46
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,080
Yeah!

47
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,080
Drink!

48
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:35,720
OK!

49
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,440
Come on.

50
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:42,120
Cheers, dude.

51
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,200
Cheers.

52
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,400
Mr. Kang, what are you up to lately?

53
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,240
Nothing special.

54
00:02:56,640 --> 00:03:00,120
I just introduce people to each other.

55
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:03,760
I'm always so kind.

56
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,040
You know that.

57
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:08,120
Yibei,

58
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,080
do you

59
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,440
remember your classmate?

60
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,840
Who?

61
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,040
The girl

62
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,880
Xu Zhaolin brought to me.

63
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,960
Miss Su Nan.

64
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:23,200
Quite an old friend. I don't remember.

65
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,160
Two years ago,

66
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,960
during your business trip
in the neighboring city,

67
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,080
you had stomach bleeding.

68
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,280
Don't you remember?

69
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,360
(Emergency Room)

70
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,200
How's he, doctor?

71
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,920
He's in an emergency

72
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,200
and needs blood transfusions.

73
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,080
His blood type is Rhesus Macacus

74
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:20,320
but we don't have any in stock.

75
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,560
Thank you.

76
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,200
I'll pay the bill, first.

77
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,200
And I'll try to get the blood.

78
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,280
Doctor,

79
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:28,920
I have this type of blood.

80
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,640
You did big blood transfusions.

81
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,680
Have some rest here.

