147
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,640
Love?

148
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,720
I don't love him.

149
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,520
What are you thinking?

150
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,840
I'll be relieved, then.

151
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,720
Don't imagine things.

152
